170
00:07:09,970 --> 00:07:11,410
so you can hire the best lawyers.

171
00:07:11,650 --> 00:07:12,660
Plus, we can utilize

172
00:07:12,660 --> 00:07:14,140
my influence in the media

173
00:07:14,740 --> 00:07:15,820
