Then, two.

204
00:08:28,020 --> 00:08:29,370
Or three?

205
00:08:30,980 --> 00:08:32,530
Four should be enough.

206
00:08:32,530 --> 00:08:34,210
It's exhausting to have babies.

207
00:08:34,210 --> 00:08:35,020
I feel bad for you.

208
00:08:35,050 --> 00:08:36,020
Thank you.

209
00:08:36,330 --> 00:08:37,850
