234
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:17,420
It's a great bargain!

235
00:09:17,420 --> 00:09:18,090
Here.

236
00:09:18,770 --> 00:09:19,500
Cheers!

237
00:09:29,290 --> 00:09:30,290
