252
00:09:59,970 --> 00:10:00,900
I'll go tomorrow.

253
00:10:02,090 --> 00:10:03,420
I'll definitely go tomorrow. Sit down.

254
00:10:18,100 --> 00:10:19,180
Let me see

255
00:10:19,180 --> 00:10:20,260
